Belden and Blake Energy Co, amaster limited partnership, said it entered into an agreementto sell 400,000 of its units for two mln dlrs in cash.    The company said &lt;Great Pacific Capital S.A.> of Geneva,Switzerland, is acting as lead manager for the privateplacement of the units with international investors.    Under the agreement, it said an option has also beengranted to buy up to 800,000 additional units at five dlrs perunit on or before July 13. Reuter&#3;